{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 9405830}, {"t": "<div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por resoluci&#xF3;n exenta N&#xBA; 388, de 30 de enero de 2014, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, modif&#xED;case el numeral 1&#xBA; de la <a href=\"https://www.leychile.cl/Navegar?idNorma=1058152&amp;idParte=&amp;idVersion=\">resoluci&#xF3;n exenta N&#xBA; 3.789, de 2013</a>, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, que estableci&#xF3; las toneladas asignadas a los Titulares de Licencias Transables de Pesca Clase A, inscritas en el Registro P&#xFA;blico que lleva esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, a ser extra&#xED;das durante el a&#xF1;o 2014, en las unidades de pesquer&#xED;a que a continuaci&#xF3;n se indican:</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Anchoveta XV-II Regiones</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/37735.jpg\">.</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Sardina Espa&#xF1;ola XV-II Regiones</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/37736.jpg\">.</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Jurel XV-II Regiones</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/37737.jpg\">.</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Achoveta III-IV Regiones</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/37738.jpg\">.</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Sardina Espa&#xF1;ola III-IV Regiones</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/37739.jpg\">.</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Jurel III-IV Regiones</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/37740.jpg\">.</div><div c